@startuml B8 Role-Specific Personalization
title B8 Slice 5 - Role-Specific Personalization

actor "Reviewer / QA / Tech Lead" as Actor
rectangle "Protocol Message\nREQUEST_CHANGES / APPROVE_IMPLEMENTATION / CLOSE_TASK" as Message
rectangle "Feedback Recorder" as Recorder
database "retrieval_feedback_events" as Feedback
database "retrieval_role_profiles" as Profiles
rectangle "Retrieval Rerank\nsource/path/symbol boost" as Rerank
database "retrieval_runs" as Runs
database "retrieval_run_hits" as Hits

Actor --> Message
Message --> Recorder
Recorder --> Runs
Recorder --> Hits
Recorder --> Feedback
Feedback --> Profiles
Profiles --> Rerank
Rerank --> Runs

note right of Profiles
Scope merge:
- global company profile
- project profile

Applied by:
- role
- eventType
- sourceType
- path
- symbol
end note

note bottom of Rerank
Explainable additive boost only.
Does not replace hybrid + graph + temporal scoring.
end note

@enduml
